ActYukon Act
PrecisTransfer, to the COMMISSIONER of the YUKON TERRITORY, of the administration and control of the entire interest of the Crown in a former oil pipeline right-of-way and in a former railway right-of-way that were granted to the British Yukon Railway Company over certain properties situated in the City of Whitehorse.
